title: Preview- Captain Marvel #1
body:
Preview- Captain Marvel #1

As Captain Marvel, Carol Danvers has spent months in space protecting Earth from alien threats big and small, but now it’s time for Earth’s mightiest hero to come home. New York City has never looked so good. But every re-entry comes with the unexpected, and Carol is about to hit a whole lot of unexpected.

It’s a fresh start and an oversized, star-studded welcome home for a hero who’s been…

summary: Here are my theories regarding the mid and post credit scenes for the upcoming Marvel Studios movie, Captain Marvel (in cinemas...
body:
Here are my theories regarding the mid and post credit scenes for the upcoming Marvel Studios movie, Captain Marvel (in cinemas March 8).

Captain Marvel is set 1995, so it will need scenes that tie it in with the previous Marvel Studios movies set in the present day.

Mid Credit Scene: Captain Marvel receives the distress signal paged by Nick Fury and heads towards the location.

Post Credit Scene: Captain Marvel arrives at the exact spot in Atlanta where she was paged by Nick Fury.

Noticing the pager on the ground and Fury nowhere to be seen, she picks up the pager and realises something major has just happened.

Captain Marvel then looks inside Fury’s car and noticing Maria Hill’s computer indicating the “multiple bogies over Wakanda”, she makes her way over there in search of answers.
